search_results.title: Movements (band)
search_results.snippet: Movements are a post-hardcore band from Rancho Santa Margarita, California, formed in 2015.

search_results.title: Pioneering Movements
search_results.snippet: Steve gives us an inspirational peek into movements and the people who lead them. – Alan Hirsch author of The Permanent Revolution

search_results.title: Social Movements: The Structure of Collective Mobilization
search_results.snippet: Social Movements cleverly translates the art of collective action and mobilization by excluded groups to facilitate understanding social change from below.
